{"tid":2447835,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國商販每月從醫院殯儀館收取孕婦胎盤加工出售  據稱進食胎盤養生效果一流","createTime":"2021-03-15T12:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T14:36:42.000Z","uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e1544d3b4024e56704226cb33e69aa69bce36d99","tid":2447835,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:55:30.000Z","msg":"夜幕降臨，廢舊的小院裏，王余環顧四周，發現沒人後，快速打開面包車後排門，戴上一次性塑料手套，從車上紙箱裏解開一個個黑色塑料袋。濃重的血腥味撲面而來，袋中是一團團帶有血沫的暗紅色新鮮人體胎盤，一些臍帶已經變紅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0DW70MZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0DW70MZ.jpg&h=49266f2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"small\">王余和記者接頭驗貨，袋子中裝滿新鮮的人體胎盤。（視頻截圖）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n人體胎盤是母體與胎兒間進行物質交換的器官，原衛生部早在2005年就以批複形式表示，&ldquo;任何單位和個人不得買賣胎盤。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n加工者稱醫院、醫廢廠、殯儀館為主要進貨渠道每月能加工上萬個胎盤出售<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jb0MwT6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJb0MwT6.jpg&h=d9e3402a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><strong>劉義給記者展示了自家作坊加工新鮮人體胎盤的圖片。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n胎盤加工成純幹貨一般需要7道工序。閆軍介紹，剝袋子、挑揀、上鍋煮、泡水去除血沫、盤好臍帶、去除周圈&ldquo;皮子&rdquo;（組織）、烘烤，最快也要4天。以前利潤高，一個可以掙10元到20元；現在加工都是靠走量掙錢，一個胎盤差不多掙5元錢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9GUhDzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9GUhDzo.jpg&h=25189e38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"small\">加工後用於進食的胎盤</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ywTFBmj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FywTFBmj.jpg&h=a1c83dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1tsOLeL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1tsOLeL.jpg&h=e30e4d42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb9db7a384920e46cf083c932ccbf82f340a71b3","tid":2447835,"uid":377617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e45736446cafa10c339322e6b95c28ea083995","tid":2447835,"uid":391580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:56:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NhTRH1H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNhTRH1H.jpg&h=da9c5091&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34b55271a2cbd68e942ddc8c84d4a28a57801993","tid":2447835,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:57:09.000Z","msg":"315暗訪｜胎盤黑市：商販稱從醫廢廠殯儀館收貨月加工萬個 <a href=\"https://c.m.163.com/news/a/G54QBOHQ0514R9P4.html?spss=newsapp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc.m.163.com%2Fnews%2Fa%2FG54QBOHQ0514R9P4.html%3Fspss%3Dnewsapp&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDjUVmWcutTvqHtF1LT7nQkc%3D&h=eed59503\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://c.m.163.com/news/a/G54QBOHQ0514R9P4.html?spss=newsapp</a>"},{"pid":"2f579e7457d611c374ce09c99faa636c4ed70229","tid":2447835,"uid":77968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:03:57.000Z","msg":"食人肉?"},{"pid":"bbe7c4006a73cfeb1c0ae52c572061808d8bc706","tid":2447835,"uid":155095,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2f579e7457d611c374ce09c99faa636c4ed70229","tid":2447835,"uid":77968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:03:57.000Z","msg":"食人肉?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:06:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5E0piDi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5E0piDi.jpg&h=514a1e6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ac493c02522b635454c5f567bd24e7cf2bfbf3a",